@startuml problem-definition-workflow
title Current workflow (AS-IS) — Course request via email → payment → invoice → completion evidence

skinparam ActivityFontSize 16
skinparam ActivityFontStyle bold
skinparam ActivityBorderWidth 2
skinparam BoxFontSize 20
skinparam NoteFontSize 14
skinparam NoteBorderWidth 2
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontColor #000000
skinparam ArrowColor #333333

<style>
activity {
  LineColor #333333
  BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
}
activityText {
  FontColor #000000
}
</style>

start

:<font color=green><b>Employee</b></font>: Compose request email (to WebAcademy mailbox);
if (CC manager?) then (yes)
  :CC manager (optional);
endif
:Send email;

:<font color=orange><b>WebAcademy</b></font>: Receive request email;
:<font color=orange><b>WebAcademy</b></font>: Review request (manual);
:<font color=orange><b>WebAcademy</b></font>: Reply approval email to Employee;

:<font color=orange><b>WebAcademy</b></font>: Schedule offline payment appointment (Employee + Finance);
note right
Scheduling channel today may be email / calendar / chat.
System goal: create a single record + timeline.
end note

:<font color=green><b>Employee</b></font>: Attend offline appointment;

:<font color=blue><b>Finance</b></font>: Attend offline appointment;
:<font color=blue><b>Finance</b></font>: Enter payment details in Coursera/Udemy;
note right
Payment is executed by Finance directly in the platform.
end note

:<font color=orange><b>WebAcademy</b></font>: Confirm enrollment/payment completed? (often implicitly);
note right
Often no single place proving "paid" vs "pending".
end note

:<font color=green><b>Employee</b></font>: Receive invoice (from Coursera/Udemy);
:<font color=green><b>Employee</b></font>: Email invoice to WebAcademy mailbox;

:<font color=orange><b>WebAcademy</b></font>: Receive invoice email;
if (Invoice handling method?) then (Forward to Finance)
  :<font color=orange><b>WebAcademy</b></font>: Forward invoice email to Finance;
  :<font color=blue><b>Finance</b></font>: Process internally (???);
  note right
Unknown: Is Finance only archiving invoice? Or creating reimbursement? Or booking cost center?
end note
else (AFAS reimbursement)
  :<font color=orange><b>WebAcademy</b></font>: Create reimbursement in AFAS (???);
  note right
Unknown: Is reimbursement always used? Who submits it: WebAcademy or Employee?
end note
endif

:<font color=green><b>Employee</b></font>: Finish course;
:<font color=green><b>Employee</b></font>: Email certificate/completion evidence to WebAcademy mailbox;

:<font color=orange><b>WebAcademy</b></font>: Receive certificate email;
:<font color=orange><b>WebAcademy</b></font>: Store certificate (???);
:<font color=orange><b>WebAcademy</b></font>: Mark completion tracked (???);
note right
Unknown today: Where certificates live (mailbox? sharepoint? drive?) And how completion is tracked (if at all).
System goal: attach certificate to the request record.
end note

stop
@enduml
